snippet.title: Last Minute Love – The Nursing Home Dating Sim (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Download it for free on itch.io: https://thephilipcal.itch.io/lastminutelove
or on GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/lastMinuteLove/391663

You play an old person who doesn't want to die alone. Romance any of the 4 residents or the nurse. Bring them items they've lost or help them with their troubles. Will you be able to find Love?
